summary:
May 23rd, 2018 elected as teacher of the year in the IPD master of the faculty Industrial Design Engineering

December 2016 my new book 'vehicle seat comfort and design' was handed over to Antje Terno of Airbus

More info: http://www.boekenbestellen.nl/boek/vehicle-seat-comfort-and-design/?lang=en
